Woojer is a Haptic Technology company, operating in the United States, Israel and Taiwan. Woojer has been granted patents for their small and powerful haptic actuator. Compact haptics have numerous applications, mainly in entertainment music, Movies, VR, AR, MR and video games. Additional applications include therapeutics and the automotive technology. The technology also enables deaf and hard of hearing to engage in activities they are usually precluded from, such as listening to music or the audio of video games.
